
<item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-rafiee-6man-local-security-03.txt'>
    <title>"Recommendations for Local Security Deployments", Hosnieh Rafiee</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-rafiee-6man-local-security-03.txt</link>
    <description>There are currently some mechanisms available to mitigate attacks in local networks -- Secure Neighbor Discovery (SeND), First Hop Security (FHS), SAVI, etc.. The purpose of this document is to compare these mechanisms and offer some recommendations regarding the implementations and deployments of these mechanisms.</description>
    <dc:date>2015-05-08T07:00:00-00:00</dc:date>
</item>
